  "title": "Permanent SSO ( Tuas South | DAY | Factory )",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Reachfield Security (Grade “A” agency) specialises in supplying security manpower to Schools, Factories, Shopping Centres, Museums, libraries, etc.</strong></em></p><p><u><strong>Senior Security Officer</strong></u></p><ul><li><strong>Salary gross up to $3430</strong></li><li><strong>Tuas South </strong></li></ul><p>////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////</p><p>1. Works in an international school environment.</p><p>2. Good customer service skills; able to communicate with people of all levels.</p><p>3. 12hrs-shift (Fixed shift, no need to rotate)</p><p>4. PC knowledge required.</p><p>5. Job duties include traffic control, issue visitors/ contractor passes, patrolling, protecting clients’ premises and access control, etc.</p><p>6. Possess valid security license, completed WSQ RTT.</p><p>Walk-in for interviews - (Mon to Fri, 9am to 5pm)</p><p>10 Anson Road #26-09</p><p>International Plaza, Singapore 079903</p><p>(Tanjong Pagar MRT)</p><p><strong>For more information, please call the office at 6324 0648 / 9137 4851 (Janet)</strong></p><p>You may fill in the application form online thru below link.</p><p>https://rss.armfort.com/direct...</p><p>Do let us know once you submit the application online</p>",
