    "description": "<p><strong>Reachfield Security &amp; Safety Management Pte Ltd is a licensed Security Guards Agency from the Singapore Police Force (SPF) &amp; established since 2003.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>We are graded \"A\" by the Police Licensing Regulatory Department (PLRD) and ISO 9001:2008 (Quality Management), ISO 22301 : 2012 (Business Continuity Management) and OHSAS 18001:2007 (Occupational Health &amp; Safety Assessment Series), Bizsafe Star certified company.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>We specialize in the provision of security service and safety service, such as the supply of security manpower, security consultancy, security system, safety manpower, equipments and supplies</strong></p>\n<p><strong>In addition, we offer complimentary value added services such as training, consultation and advice.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>We strive to provide effective security and safety solutions to professional organizations.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Towards our clients, we deliver services that surpass your expectations. Towards our staff, we treat each staff with respect and provide professional security training.</strong></p>",
